  "texts": [
    "The 'Methodology' section outlines the systematic review conducted to identify the practical resources and tools that multidisciplinary teams can use when developing systems.",
    "Likewise, a detailed explanation of the creation of a graph incorporating multiple typologies to classify the tools discovered is provided.",
    "The 'Results' section exposes the main findings of incorporating the tools in the typologies.",
    "The 'Limitations and Future Work' section highlights ideas that may help close the gap for implementing AI ethics and the limitations of this review.",
    "Lastly, the study concludes by presenting the challenges that need to be addressed to create AI that benefits society."
